        "text": "DATES: The sale will take place on September 12, 2024, at 8:00 a.m., Pacific Time, on the EnergyNet website at: https://www.EnergyNet.com/govt_ listing.pl. Submit written comments regarding the sale until August 26, 2024. The BLM will publish this Notice of Realty Action once a week for three consecutive weeks in the Lincoln County Record and Ely Times newspapers. Prior to the sale, a sales matrix will be published on the following website: https:// www.EnergyNet.com/govt_listing.pl. The sales matrix provides information specific to each sale parcel such as legal description, physical location, encumbrances, acreage, and FMV. The FMV for each parcel will be available in the sales matrix at least 30 days prior to",
